                           <bibl>On the text and for references see <title rend="italic">PAL</title>, no. 81.</bibl>
                        </listBibl>
                        <note>
                           Because of the excision of two leaves the text ends incomplete in ch. 76, edn. 164/50, with the loss of thirteen lines of printed text. 
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     
